{"tid":946662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 假招聘呃文件申借貸　4人落網涉款58萬元","createTime":"2018-12-18T16:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T07:28:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76c0744ad27afb50e914c1dceb03d5680bd60681","tid":946662,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:26:35.000Z","msg":"警方於今年6至8月期間，接獲3名本地男子（19至29歲）報案，指有人向他們聲稱能夠提供工作機會，並要求<span style=\"color: red;\">提交住址證明及身份證明文件副本</span>，受害人遂按指示提交文件，詎料3人及後收到銀行信件並發現欠下款項，懷疑受騙遂報案，3人被騙款項合共約58萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方經深入調查，發現有人利用受害人的個人資料，向不同銀行申請貸款及信用卡，並騙走款項，警方於今日（18日）在大嶼山區及深水埗區，以涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」拘捕3男1女（17至43歲），帶署扣查。行動中，警方檢獲電腦、電話、大量銀行借貸文件及信用卡等證物，案件交由大嶼山警區刑事調查隊跟進，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181218/bkn-20181218180936064-1218_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181218%2Fbkn-20181218180936064-1218_00822_001.html&d=jrtsyvjcMbw9rH99mlC5lDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e79b9e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181218/bkn-20181218180936064-1218_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b80f2d3a55093d37d486c431a77fee25521695bd","tid":946662,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"Job Interview? 不了"},{"pid":"28ccf5b757995a7e7415c327d37aa16eb3411d67","tid":946662,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"肯定係扮啲乜尻絕世荀工啦<br />\n然後啲傻仔貪心"},{"pid":"bb07df325a19b772deaad69eff19d39c1686cc5c","tid":946662,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e581da758230d9f1aefbe01610662311074d71","tid":946662,"uid":165213,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"28ccf